data.description:
Discover a rare gem with this unique property, situated on a cul-de-sac just moments from the vibrant heart of Downtown Henderson. Boasting a generous 1/4-acre size with RV parking, this home offers an exceptional opportunity to customize your dream home. The expansive backyard is a perfect opportunity to create your own haven for relaxation and entertainment. 
Ideally located near the thriving Water Street District, this residence combines prime location with affordability – a rare combination in today's market. Enjoy the open layout with a kitchen ready for your personal touch. The primary bathroom awaits with a spacious garden tub illuminated by a skylight, adding a touch of luxury to your daily retreat. Save on energy costs with included solar panels. Whether you're envisioning this property for personal use or as a savvy investment, the potential is limitless. Don't let this extraordinary opportunity pass you by – secure this unique property while you can!
